    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丧尸病毒突然爆发，世界成为一片废墟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将作为这个世界中深陷危险的幸存者，克服周围的各种威胁，揭开丧尸病毒的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>栩栩如生的广阔开放世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/0a0b6725f40da19297521e5eb226d69a.poster.avif?t=1758605692\" width=620 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/0a0b6725f40da19297521e5eb226d69a.webm?t=1758605692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在《暗夜绝望》的无缝开放世界中探索每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在恍若真实的世界中，体验超绝沉浸感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在充满死亡气息的荒凉村庄桑德克里克，开始属于你的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从沙漠村庄，到冰雪岛屿，再到休闲度假城市，你可以尽情探索各种主题的开放世界，破解丧尸病毒的根源，创造属于你自己的生存故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开放世界中生存所需的各种交通工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/33f394b9aca23852d5620efc8cca764a.poster.avif?t=1758605692\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/33f394b9aca23852d5620efc8cca764a.webm?t=1758605692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了探索《暗夜绝望》的广阔的开放世界，你可以使用多种车辆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从末日来临之前的普通家用车，到拥有强大体积和力量的卡车、警车、救护车等特殊车辆，都可以加以利用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >车辆不仅可以用来撞开挡路的丧尸，还可以作为强大装备进行改装，迎接末世的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在丧尸的无尽威胁中生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/a8c0973ecec1a3ea8b70877101635614.poster.avif?t=1758605692\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/a8c0973ecec1a3ea8b70877101635614.webm?t=1758605692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在以大规模丧尸爆发后的末世为背景的《暗夜绝望》中，各种恐怖的丧尸对你构成了严峻的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们以威胁性的动作和攻击性，有时使用多样的战斗方式来攻击你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了对抗丧尸，你必须动用一切可用的手段。你可以通过精准的瞄准射击逐个消灭，或者使用强大的投掷武器横扫丧尸群。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与居民一起打造独属于你的避难所</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/e5de6c0f41469744395bbe0a5c52e001.poster.avif?t=1758605692\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/e5de6c0f41469744395bbe0a5c52e001.webm?t=1758605692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在危机四伏的末世中，你可以建造一个为了生存自给自足的避难所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在避难所招募末世中生存下来的各式幸存者，与他们一同创建社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和他们一起努力活下去，建造各种设施，解锁新功能，建设更安全的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募的居民既能投入生产，提高避难所的效率，又能加入战斗和探索，强化战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富多样且紧凑的多人体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/7e8b2add1f223982adf9e12d911a738e.poster.avif?t=1758605692\" width=620 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548520/extras/7e8b2add1f223982adf9e12d911a738e.webm?t=1758605692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《暗夜绝望》中除了紧张刺激的单人模式，还能体验到高密度的多人模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以与其他玩家们一起在无尽尸潮中生存，也可以联手击杀恐怖的突变巨型丧尸获得奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，与他人合作并不是唯一的生存方式。 前往远征，可以在战斗区域与多名玩家竞争收集资源，体验紧张十足的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存，从没有标准答案。</p>",
